All,
I am solving a diffusion equation with energy equation (temperature).
I am writing a C++ class that inherits from Material. My program looks like the one below,
where "time" is the computation time, "del_time" is the time step size.
Please let me know how to get "temperature," "time" and "time step size."
float base, temp, flux, del_time, temperature;
float constant_A = 10, constant_B = 100, constant_C = 1000;
If (time <= 0)
base = 0;
if (temperature <= 100)
temp = constant_A * temperature;
else
temp = constant_B * temperature;
base = base + (temp * del_time);
flux = constant_C / base;
Sincerely,
Thomas
